&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Ticketing Meeting Preparation Agent&lt;/strong&gt; that gathers relevant sales insights, CRM data, and historical context to help ticketing teams prepare for client meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Early prototypes of a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Generalized &quot;AI Coworker&quot; agent&lt;/strong&gt; capable of assisting teams across departments with research, reporting, and operational tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
